== Abstract Syntax Tree ==
LogicalSink(table=[default_catalog.default_database.MyMTTable], fields=[a, b, c])
+- LogicalProject(a=[CAST($0):BIGINT], b=[$1], c=[$2])
   +- LogicalTableScan(table=[[default_catalog, default_database, MyTable]])

== Optimized Physical Plan ==
Sink(table=[default_catalog.default_database.MyMTTable], fields=[a, b, c])
+- Calc(select=[CAST(a AS BIGINT) AS a, b, c])
   +- TableSourceScan(table=[[default_catalog, default_database, MyTable]], fields=[a, b, c])

== Optimized Execution Plan ==
